  "prompt": "What are the things you should do for your best friend?",
  "response": "Here are some things you should do for your best friend:\n\n1. Be supportive\n- Listen without judgment\n- Offer emotional support during tough times\n- Celebrate their achievements\n\n2. Be honest and trustworthy\n- Tell the truth\n- Keep their secrets\n- Be reliable\n\n3. Show genuine care\n- Check in regularly\n- Remember important dates\n- Ask about their life and feelings\n\n4. Spend quality time together\n- Make time for shared activities\n- Have meaningful conversations\n- Create memories\n\n5. Be loyal\n- Stand up for them\n- Defend them when needed\n- Remain committed to the friendship\n\n6. Respect boundaries\n- Understand their personal space\n- Don't pressure them\n- Accept their choices\n\n7. Offer help\n- Assist during challenging times\n- Provide practical support\n- Be available when they need you\n\n8. Show appreciation\n- Express gratitude\n- Acknowledge their value in your life\n- Give compliments\n\n9. Be forgiving\n- Understand nobody's perfect\n- Work through disagreements\n- Don't hold grudges\n\n10. Have fun together\n- Laugh\n- Share enjoyable experiences\n- Keep the friendship light and enjoyable\n\nThese actions help maintain a strong, healthy friendship based on mutual respect and care.",
